DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is compare the safety and pharmacokinetic characteristics of HD203 liquid with those of etanercept (enbrel) prefilled injection after subcutaneous injection.
DOC.brief_title: Safety and Pharmacokinetic Characteristics of HD203 Liq. in Healthy Subjects
